The evidence with the title '6 historic structures in America that were built by slaves ' says Jul 26, 2016  ... Back in 2012 , former speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi teamed up with party leaders in Congress to unveil a commemorative marker in the Capitol Visitors Center to pay tribute to the black men and women who constructed it . She said the marker acted as amemorial to the “ tragedy and sin ” of slavery . 
